{"tid":711532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Instagram每月活躍用戶破10億 藉全新服務IGTV吸引更多使用黏著","createTime":"2018-06-21T15:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:24:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ae937e2932e1698b6170af66122e9986f9f64079","tid":711532,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"稍早於舊金山舉辦活動中，Instagram宣布旗下每月活躍用戶已經突破10億人，成為Facebook另一個每月活躍用戶人數達10億人規模的應用服務。而為了吸引更多人使用，Instagram也推出全新獨立影音應用服務IGTV，並且在原本的Instagram服務中提供串接，透過各類影音內容增加使用者觀看黏著度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/mashdigi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-20180619-KS-pamelachen-IMG_0157-2160_lo.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmashdigi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F02-20180619-KS-pamelachen-IMG_0157-2160_lo.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26ssl%3D1&h=6ef6ebda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與先前已經在Instagram推出最多1分鐘長度的短影片形式不同，IGTV提供不限影音長度的拍攝效果，同時使用者也能像YouTube擁有個人專屬頻道，並且與Instagram帳戶連動，一旦粉絲選擇追蹤特定對象，即可連帶追蹤其IGTV頻道內容。<br />\n<br />\n而與一般影音平台不同，IGTV將著重與手機裝置結合，因此拍攝風格也會以直向影片內容為主，並且讓整體畫面以手機螢幕最大範圍呈現。在觀看介面中，IGTV欲社會自動播放隨選影音內容，使用者也能透過「推薦 (For You)」、「追蹤 (Following)」、「熱門 (Popular)」，以及「繼續觀看 (Continue Watching)」分類觀看不同影音內容，同時也能在影音內容底下留言回應，或是轉發分享給他人觀看。<br />\n <br />\nInstagram預期將能藉由IGTV讓使用人數繼續成長，同時預期未來也會藉由IGTV服務形式銜接更多廣告宣傳業務，甚至也預期結合更多名人、內容創作效益，持續吸引更多用戶觀看黏著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/mashdigi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2-Watch-2UP-EN.png?w=1024&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmashdigi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2-Watch-2UP-EN.png%3Fw%3D1024%26ssl%3D1&h=469ca972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/mashdigi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/3-ChannelProfile-2UP-EN.png?w=1024&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmashdigi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F3-ChannelProfile-2UP-EN.png%3Fw%3D1024%26ssl%3D1&h=92c89749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mashdigi.com/?p=76845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmashdigi.com%2F%3Fp%3D76845&d=6Agar0zoNWVtdaUxWX%2Fl6TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=080ca6f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mashdigi.com/?p=76845</a>"},{"pid":"717c32252ee1ec73facb846f55086ae4ea0e35d4","tid":711532,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/231701_6e1730c594b0ffb312fcb5158708e2b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F231701_6e1730c594b0ffb312fcb5158708e2b1.png&h=e71138f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSocial network係文明淪陷嘅始作俑者"},{"pid":"36dc2acbcf9920abffb5256692b3f8a8e0cc18ef","tid":711532,"uid":25952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"而家多廣告到仆街 仲搞埋晒d垃圾"},{"pid":"cb1dc5dff22a5f2cb02f62d74810bf068a925e64","tid":711532,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"好戇鳩 愈搞愈同質化<br />\n限時動態 做live 宜家搞埋igtv<br />\n一禁入去d制愈加愈多 好快成個畫面都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21723d1d90fce8afe7a2095607e1cf46ecfeed37","tid":711532,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cb1dc5dff22a5f2cb02f62d74810bf068a925e64","tid":711532,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"好戇鳩 愈搞愈同質化<br />\n限時動態 做live 宜家搞埋igtv<br />\n一禁入去d制愈加愈多 好快成個畫面都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"igtv要另外下載app"},{"pid":"9d8dc860f7033fbd7ec2aa492cbd4539ae183e8d","tid":711532,"uid":9175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21723d1d90fce8afe7a2095607e1cf46ecfeed37","tid":711532,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cb1dc5dff22a5f2cb02f62d74